Author: Altay Özaygen [aut, cre], Keoungoui Kim [ctb]
Maintainer: Altay Özaygen <altay.ozaygen@gmail.com>
Description: This package downloads WIOD data, then creates yearly long
    tables. It also aggregates the manufacturing industry with respect
    to its technological intensity, a Eurostat categorization of the
    manufacturing industry. WIOD files are from 2000 to 2014, they include
    56 industries from 44 countries and the rest of the world (RoW). WIOD
    data also comprises final consumption data, VA values, etc.
